message: "If you use this work, please cite it as below."
title: "Distilling a Vision-Language Model into a Compact Food Classifier"
abstract: >-
  A reproducible study of vision-language-model-as-annotator knowledge
  distillation: an open VLM (Qwen2-VL) pseudo-labels Food-101 images, a compact
  CNN student is trained on those labels only, and accuracy is evaluated against
  the teacher and an oracle student trained on ground-truth labels.
